h5. Summary:
Can a feature to record the last few times JIRA was indexed be added directly into JIRA so that the data is updated whenever JIRA indexes itself or is indexed by the Admin?

This information can be useful for the JIRA administrator.

*Current Workaround*
- Proceed to {{JIRA HOME > Cache > Indexes}}
- Check when last this folder was modified.

_This would work just fine however it would be inaccurate if the folder is modified from outside JIRA._

